title: Extended Classic: Cosmic Queries: Venus with Dr. FunkySpoon
description: Astrobiologist Dr. David Grinspoon and Leighann Lord answer questions from fans about Venus. NEW: 13-minute “Venusian Update” from Dr. FunkySpoon and Chuck Nice about Japan’s “never say die” Akatsuki orbiter and future US missions to our “Evil Twin.”
author: feed@startalkradio.net (Neil deGrasse Tyson)
